            <h1 class=3D"title">Unit Conversions (Part 2):</h1>
            <h1>Perform Unit Conversions for Speeds</h1>
            <p>When we do unit conversions for speed, we have units in the =
numerator and denominator that we need to change to what we want. The proce=
ss is exactly the same, we just need to watch 2 sets of units. The followin=
g video will explain how to do this by doing an example problem:</p>

