            <p>Steps for Speeds Unit Conversions</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Start with what you know (On top and bottom)</li>
                <li>Determine what you want to get in the end. (On top and =
bottom.)</li>
                <li>Determine what conversion factor(s) to use. You will ne=
ed more than one. (at least one for the top and one for the bottom)</li>
                <li>Multiply by 1 in the form of the conversion factor that=
 cancels out the unwanted units.</li>
            </ol>

